SQL_STMT_U.val: select count (projekt_id) from Projekt p WITH(NOLOCK) inner join ro_kontaktpersonen k WITH(NOLOCK) on (k.Ebene1=p.Ebene1 and k.Ebene2=p.Ebene2 and k.Ebene3=p.Ebene3 and k.Ebene4=p.Ebene4 and k.ProjektNr=p.Projekt_ID) where p.Ebene1=:1 and p.Ebene2=:2 and p.Ebene3=:3 and p.Ebene4=:4 and p.aktiv=1 and k.EMail=':5'
